---
import aboutMeImage from '../../../assets/about-me.webp'
import { Mail, Phone } from '@lucide/astro'
---

<section
  id='sobre-mi'
  class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32'>


  <!-- Titan One watermark -->
  <div class="font-display pointer-events-none absolute -right-8 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none"
    aria-hidden='true'>
    SEO
  </div>

  <!-- Orange geometric accent -->
  <div
    class='absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1.5 h-40 bg-teal rounded-r-full pointer-events-none'
    aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div class='mx-auto max-w-[1280px] px-5'>
    <div
      data-animate-direction='left'
      class='grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center'>

      <!-- Photo column -->
      <div class='relative flex justify-center lg:justify-start flex-shrink-0'>

        <!-- Stacked background rects for depth -->
        <div
          class='absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-teal/10 border border-teal/20'
          aria-hidden='true'></div>
        <div
          class='absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-full h-full rounded-2xl bg-teal/8 border border-teal/20'
          aria-hidden='true'></div>

        <img
          src={aboutMeImage.src}
          width={aboutMeImage.width}
          height={aboutMeImage.height}
          loading='lazy'
          alt='Salvador Jesús, consultor SEO freelance en Barcelona'
          class='relative aspect-4/5 w-56 sm:w-64 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-2xl shadow-charcoal/15 ring-1 ring-surface/5'
        />

        <!-- Orange corner dot -->
        <div
          class='absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-teal shadow-sm shadow-teal/40'
          aria-hidden='true'></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content column -->
      <div class='space-y-7 max-w-xl'>

        <!-- Eyebrow label -->
        <div class='flex items-center gap-3'>
          <span class='h-px w-8 bg-teal flex-shrink-0'></span>
          <span
            class='text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-teal'>
            Quizás te estés preguntando
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Name + Role -->
        <div class='space-y-1.5'>
          <p
            class='font-display text-[clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3.25rem)] font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-cream'
>
            ¿Quién demonios soy?
          </p>
          <h2 class='text-base font-medium text-teal tracking-wide'>
            Consultor SEO freelance en Barcelona
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Accent rule -->
        <div class='flex items-center'>
          <div class='h-px w-16 bg-teal'></div>
          <div class='h-px w-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal/40 to-transparent'></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <p class='text-base/7 text-cream/70 text-pretty'>
          Me llamo Salva y hago que los negocios locales dejen de ser invisibles en Google. Soy muy analítico, así que todo lo que hago se mide: más llamadas, más mensajes, más presupuestos. Si se puede medir, se puede mejorar.
        </p>
        <p class='text-base/7 text-cream/70 text-pretty'>
          Si tu negocio depende de clientes cercanos, mi servicio de <a href='/seo-local-barcelona/' class='text-teal font-medium hover:text-sage/80 underline decoration-teal/30 underline-offset-2 transition-colors'>consultor SEO local en Barcelona</a> se enfoca en Google Maps y búsquedas con intención geográfica para que te encuentren primero.
        </p>

        <!-- Tool badges -->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2'>
          {
            [
              'Google Search Console',
              'Google Analytics 4',
              'Keyword Planner',
              'WordPress',
              'Elementor Pro',
              'Yoast SEO',
              'DinoRank',
            ].map((tool) => (
              <span class='inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-cream ring-1 ring-inset ring-teal/20'>
                {tool}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <hr class='border-teal/15' />

        <!-- Contact links -->
        <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-4'>
          <a
            href='mailto:salvadorjesus.seo@gmail.com'
            class='group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-cream hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-200'>
            <span
              class='flex h-9 w-9 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cream ring-1 ring-teal/15 group-hover:bg-sage/5 group-hover:ring-teal/20 transition-all duration-200'>
              <Mail class='h-4 w-4' />
            </span>
            salvadorjesus.seo@gmail.com
          </a>

          <a
            href='tel:+34692051399'
            class='group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-cream hover:text-sage transition-colors duration-200'>
            <span
              class='flex h-9 w-9 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-cream ring-1 ring-teal/15 group-hover:bg-sage/5 group-hover:ring-teal/20 transition-all duration-200'>
              <Phone class='h-4 w-4' />
            </span>
            +34 692 051 399
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
